ng overdue critical assessment of Ciano’s famous diary, one of the most important texts from the period. Using visual materials such as photographs and films as sources and not just as illustrative material, Tobias Hof allows us to rethink our understanding of fascism and offers a new perspective on the history of fascist Italy.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aDiplomatszItalyvBiography. 0aFascismzItalyxHistoryy20th century. 0aFascistszItalyvBiography. 0aForeign ministerszItalyvBiography. 7aHISTORY / Europe / Italy.2bisacsh  aBenito Mussolini.  aGaleazzo Ciano.  aGaleazzo Ciano’s diaries.  aItalian fascism.  aSecond World War.  aWWII.  aWorld War Two.  abiography.  afascist oligarchy.  ainternational relations.  atwentieth-century Italian history.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishz978311075408708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE History 2021z9783110753851oZDB-23-DEG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311073922040uhttps://doi.org/10.3138/978148753730240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781487537302423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781487537302/original  a978-3-11-073922-0  University of Toronto Press Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-075400-1  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishb2021  a978-3-11-075408-7  EBOOK PACKAGE History 2021 Englishb2021  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11S